data.description: Nestled on 10 acres, this haven for nature enthusiasts boasts a gated rock entrance leading to a picturesque oasis with a large pond, hog-wired fencing, a barndo, main home, cottage, and storage buildings. The barndo, with alder woodworking, cathedral ceiling, and rock fireplace, offers 2 beds, 2 baths, RV storage, covered storage, and a loft. The classic Georgian main residence features 3 beds, 2 baths, a gourmet kitchen, and inviting porches for serene countryside moments. A charming cottage-style home with a kitchen, bathroom, and laundry adds to the property's allure. A fully equipped party barn, meticulously spray foamed, includes AC/heat, a kitchen, bar, bath, and an expansive outdoor entertaining area with hot tub, fire pit, and a bar. This property seamlessly blends rustic charm with modern amenities, creating a unique retreat for those seeking comfort and nature. Private tours are recommended to truly appreciate the property's extensive features beyond what pictures reveal.
